The base pipeline layer (Chainable, Builder, Pipeline, Processor) in this gem
was extracted and adapted from image_processing 1.14.0. The original
Chainable DSL, Builder immutability semantics, Pipeline orchestration, and
abstract Processor contract are preserved; only the namespace was renamed
(ImageProcessing -> Pura::Processing) and the autoloads for the Vips /
MiniMagick backends were removed. Individual source files carry a header
comment pointing back to the upstream version they were adapted from.

